#id=1
#text=I decided my backyard needed another tree .
#id=2
#text=So I went to the tree nursery and picked out a tree that I liked .
#id=3
#text=I rented a pickup truck to bring the tree home .
#id=4
#text=I loaded the tree into the truck and drove it to my house .
#id=5
#text=I grabbed a shovel from my garage , and I dug a hole in my backyard where I wanted the tree to go .
#id=6
#text=I poured some special tree fertilizer into the hole that I had bought from the tree nursery .
#id=7
#text=I then asked a friend to help me , because the tree was very big and heavy .
#id=8
#text=Together we placed the tree in the hole .
#id=9
#text=I then started to fill up the dirt around the tree .
#text=Halfway through filling it , I took a garden hose and poured water down the hole .
#text=When the water settled , I finished filling in the dirt .
#text=Over the dirt I placed a nice bed of mulch around the tree .
#text=I watered the tree once more , then stepped back to admire my work .
